rComments: Prof Ying was clear in his teaching except his accent made it hard to understand sometimes. He was very helpful when he was going over the whole course at the very last class and hinted what type of questions are most likely to come up.
Peng does a good job explaining, helpful if you sit near the class just because he isn't the loudest nor the best chalkboard writer. Pretty decent lectures, nice pacing.
